"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:00:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b9e4f0c7e0b1957eb7176af0ead56e3b24055f4","tid":1468424,"uid":23256,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:02:21.000Z","msg":"和理狗 感化自己人最叻<br />\n黑狗有棍就走最撚快 走上前排感化囉<br />\n預撚左俾人屌分化撚 <br />\n經過我以後唔會再出 救人都俾人屌搞亂機場和平 <br />\n<br />\n咪用和理非把閪口睇下 黑狗捉人你感唔感化到佢囉<br />\n黑狗捉人拉到個人走 仲要俾班和理狗割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隨便話我中計撚分化撚 我只係知最撚阻左運動進行係和理狗<br />\n媽呀 琴日以眼還眼<br />\n今日尻毛都未甩一條就唔好打 搞亂和平機場 咁同黑狗打人有咩分別<br />\n屌你老母 我呸 <br />\n以後唔會再出 當我中計 係呀我中計都係因為你班和理人割同屌人咁撚快<br />\n死係黑狗手上都甘心 痛快 <br />\n死係和理狗手上 寧轉頭仲要俾你插2刀"},{"pid":"0ef56f1de31b9d9d0c604ad135c1ce8cbc4a2ef7","tid":1468424,"uid":277589,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/excLwCu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FexcLwCu.png&h=540ef96c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n郁啲就割蓆屌自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好啦，變笑柄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0fbf358a39615d5d9bed9f5a0c3c9818312de3","tid":1468424,"uid":85734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:02:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa9a0aadf18b73eca02bef59327861b30b2d0786","tid":1468424,"uid":158889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ef56f1de31b9d9d0c604ad135c1ce8cbc4a2ef7","tid":1468424,"uid":277589,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/excLwCu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FexcLwCu.png&h=540ef96c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n郁啲就割蓆屌自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好啦，變笑柄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 