/>\n<br />\n如果出現失誤唔去承認，唔去反省，唔尊重對方互相指罵，只會不斷重複失誤，人數會變少，最後重演2014年雨革失敗歷史。"},{"pid":"68c429295a8479841b70cdfb24c206bf65093f73","tid":1468424,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:09:27.000Z","msg":"pisj"},{"pid":"470f38a11b3a68d96689c411fd87e020d00f5656","tid":1468424,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ef56f1de31b9d9d0c604ad135c1ce8cbc4a2ef7","tid":1468424,"uid":277589,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/excLwCu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FexcLwCu.png&h=540ef96c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n郁啲就割蓆屌自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好啦，變笑柄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:12:19.000Z","msg":"共媒認證割蓆分化篤灰狗就係鬼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f5529318225cb0167a3e7734c71c4db1f79156","tid":1468424,"uid":1739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:14:12.000Z","msg":"係所有野既大前提最重要既唔係指出任何錯處/ 反省<br />\n而係 「士氣」 之所以士氣最緊要<br />\n我地可以參考黑警果句： 你地無做錯！ <br />\n穩定軍心後再討論 用平心靜氣既言詞去討論為之重要。"},{"pid":"140c265b9bec1ff55035780427c0bc6b394ecb63","tid":1468424,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:17:56.000Z","msg":"打狗同公安係無問題<br />\n呢樣我相信無人會反對<br />\n<br />\n但的確有阻到一部分要走既乘客<br />\n同佢地歉意同解釋<br />\n起碼等佢地知道，民意唔好走咁多"}]}